DOC.brief_summary: This randomize double-blind crossover study pharmacokinetics , pharmacodynamics safety BCD-066 ( darbepoetin alfa manufacture CJSC BIOCAD , Russia ) Aranesp® ( Amgen Europe B.V. , Netherlands ) healthy volunteer . The purpose study demonstrate equivalence pharmacokinetics , pharmacodynamics safety parameter single subcutaneous intravenous injection . Each drug administer volunteer dose 1 µg per kilogram single subcutaneous intravenous injection interval least 25 day .
